headline: DAT: Typical May truckload rates, volumes masked tariff turmoil
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., June 19, 2025--Spot truckload van and refrigerated freight volumes rose modestly in May as shippers positioned inventory ahead of summer and potential tariffs, said DAT Freight & Analytics, which operates the DAT One freight marketplace and DAT iQ data analytics service.
